{"tid":1164901,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[三杉淳復活] 米迦勒「標童」師公上身喝走接引天使救回三杉淳","createTime":"2019-05-21T12:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T17:37:11.000Z","uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0859ef475281fcba3d7c6d460749bda16c06e83a","tid":1164901,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hereisworldball/posts/2325105891061247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhereisworldball%2Fposts%2F2325105891061247&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=3d45b495\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hereisworldball/posts/2325105891061247</a><br />\n<br />\n科幻漫畫 - 《足球小將》上期講到心臟有事嘅「球場王子」三杉淳用心口硬檔史奈達嘅凌空火焰射球。<br />\n<br />\n但係日本隊仍然失波之餘，三杉仲要心臟停頓，疑似靈魂出竅俯視瞓咗喺球場上嘅自己，引嚟一眾讀者哀鴻遍野兼網上討伐作者高橋陽一。<br />\n<br />\n不過各位唔使擔心，最新一話講到西班牙代表、識得「思維車盤球」（唔知咩嚟就真係要睇下：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1641797416058768/posts/1990855654486274?s=100027911059420&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1641797416058768%2Fposts%2F1990855654486274%3Fs%3D100027911059420%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=99978f6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1641797416058768/posts/1990855654486274?s=100027911059420&amp;sfns=mo</a>）嘅米迦勒，眼見三杉暈到之後，突然變咗《權力遊戲》嘅最終贏家布蘭&middot;史塔克，之後眉頭一皺，計上心頭，左腳踏地，大叫一聲：老師公大顯威靈！<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n震走哂本身同三杉一齊俯視自己嘅小天使之餘，仲令心臟停頓嘅三杉醒返添。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>#天使長即係天使長<br />\n#那在基督裡死了的人必先復活</strong><br />\n<br />\n- 列奧C<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：洛迪高朋友Whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28dZtyF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28dZtyF.jpg&h=bf694352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzkEtyG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzkEtyG.jpg&h=0898edb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imeRjFk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimeRjFk.jpg&h=480553b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b9014c856f3b26525c613695f91807d61be2bdc","tid":1164901,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/thailog.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/026bc675bda1f06b11382b9de0324b6e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fthailog.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F01%2F026bc675bda1f06b11382b9de0324b6e.gif&h=bb9c30c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97fefcf581ececb224adbd9ec5f58825f3143404","tid":1164901,"uid":12500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"點解劇透足球小將唔洗bam?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4c2a5d37211f102905842129d0416e5a7ac306","tid":1164901,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97fefcf581ececb224adbd9ec5f58825f3143404","tid":1164901,"uid":12500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"點解劇透足球小將唔洗bam?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b17be1e8e1fc64ac4bdcafa9a6d175af18c00d","tid":1164901,"uid":60299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f170fdb4ecb647fab749e25ad1faa62fb54a4a76","tid":1164901,"uid":31848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"c5c34157074fa92c21ec5167f8916fbdaf77bd5f","tid":1164901,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175cdd3a29ae0237d2ea4f345b3203d6dbf82374","tid":1164901,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dis